data.description: This elegant 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home features dual master suites - one on each floor - for multi generational living or guest accommodations. The main level offers an open concept living area, ideal for entertaining, while the upstairs introduces another spacious master and a vesatile loft, perfect as a home office or play area. Nestled in a prime location near Metro Park Splash Pad and schools, this residence combines convenience with luxury, making it a ''must see''. Schedule your tour today!
